Job Description
Share
And we're looking for more people like this to join our friendly and professional team. Set on the banks of the creek and along the Links Championship Golf Course, Crowne Plaza Hotel is located at on one of the country's most ambitious developments, Yas Island. The close proximity to the airport and only 40 minutes into Abu Dhabi City makes this prime location an easy accessible choice for business and leisure travellers. We are currently looking to recruit a Commis 1 to join our Kitchen team. You are required to ensure that the set up (mise en place) is ready on time and sufficient, according the instructions of the chef de partie. You will also assist in preparation of all food items and help in running the assigned station efficiently. You will need to be experienced in Arabic Cuisine. You also need to be fluent in English and flexible with working hours. In return we offer competitive pay and benefits, and a chance to work with a great team of talented people. Most importantly, we'll give you the Room to be yourself.
